The following preferences are available to be configured via the 'set' command:

auto_tune - what channels, if any, to auto-tune upon login
Default: all

biff - receive mail notifications.
Default: on
Options: on/off

colour - whether to use colour in the game.
Default: off
Options: on/off

combat_hit_colour - what colour to use for combat hits.
Default: unset

combat_miss_colour - what colour to use for combat misses.
Default: unset

email - your email address.
Default: unset

gmcp - whether to use GMCP.
Default: on
Options: on/off

highlight - whether to highlight items in a long description.
Default: on
Options: on/off

highlight_colour - what colour to use for highlighted items.
Default: 243

keepalive - whether to send keepalive messages.
Default: on
Options: on/off

morelines - the number of lines to display before paging.
Default: 20

page_display - how to display pages.
Default: percent
Options: percent/lines

prompt - what prompt to use.
Default: >

screenreader - whether you are using a screenreader.
Default: off
Options: on/off

unicode - whether to use unicode characters.
Default: on
Options: on/off
